{"tid":597094,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】中華文化點譯？","createTime":"2018-03-18T09:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T04:35:09.000Z","uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4be1a35beb6b4ee92237c9a71b39d7281e1f9d90","tid":597094,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"咁首先要講本質係咩啦，中華文化好似同中國文化有啲唔同？<br />\n<br />\n咩叫中國文化？係咪而家係中國領土一部分既都可以叫做中國文化？西藏個啲唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係哈爾濱同廣東文化都唔同，係咪兩者都可以叫做中國文化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁中華文化又係咩呢？<br />\n中原文化？嶺南文化？<br />\n<br />\nChinese culture 係 monoculture 定係 multiculture？口口聲聲話要保存中華文化既人可唔可以話我知，究竟係要保存啲乜嘢？同埋中華文化究竟點譯作英文？"},{"pid":"e810fc37ec9c9991f071eff39556a3791335e542","tid":597094,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"Han Culture"},{"pid":"4c90fdc289e60511fabba8f755468cc4c61b4324","tid":597094,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e810fc37ec9c9991f071eff39556a3791335e542","tid":597094,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"Han Culture"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"漢族沙文主義？"},{"pid":"c395e567df3d21ca32cd6bbdebb0df684958aad6","tid":597094,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c90fdc289e60511fabba8f755468cc4c61b4324","tid":597094,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e810fc37ec9c9991f071eff39556a3791335e542","tid":597094,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"Han Culture"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"漢族沙文主義？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"Han Culture係漢文化"},{"pid":"f66b0851772bcb371d32e6359d677525a46e32d7","tid":597094,"uid":12633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:25:01.00